OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNigeria pauses             
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcontroversial expatriate   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ftax                        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Nigeria has paused a controversial     
OL,6, annual levy that would require         
OL,7, businesses employing expatriates to pay
OL,8, $15,000 (#12,000) for a director and   
OL,9, $10,000 (#8,000) for other workers.    
OL,11,FPresident Bola Tinubu imposed the tax  
OL,12,Fover a week ago, but it was met with   
OL,13,Fwidespread condemnation.               
OL,15,FThe Ministry of Interior said on X the 
OL,16,Flevy would be paused for "dialogue     
OL,17,Famong stakeholders".                   
OL,19,FIt comes after a meeting was held to   
OL,20,Fdiscuss the levy on Friday in Abuja.   
